Package: federalregister.gov
Title: Federal Register API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Federal Register API. Search
    documents (rules, proposed rules, notices, presidential documents),
    fetch individual documents, list agencies, and browse public inspection
    documents. Includes LLM context injection via fr_context().
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    dplyr,
    tibble
